         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">11th September 1857 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ In reply to the application made by the Bailiff of the Botanic Gardens, ¶  in his letter addressed to you dated 31st Ulto ¶  I have the honor to inform you that as his p...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.09.11</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 57/2931, unit 4, p. 16, VPRS 975/P1 outward registered correspondence, VA 669 Public Works Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">11th September 1857</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reply to the application made by the Bailiff of the Botanic Gardens,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">P. Martyn.</p>
               </note> in his letter addressed to you dated 31st Ulto<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note> I have the honor to inform you that as his pay has already been increased from 8/ to 10/. p diem, with quarters Mr Moore<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">David Moore.</p>
               </note> is not disposed to sanction the payment of a higher rate.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">(Signed) T. C. Balmain.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director of the Botanic Gardens</p>
         </div>
      </body>
